酒店過夜<br />\n第二日就有本雜誌爆料話咩比人言語暴力<br />\n想離婚好耐<br />\n資料來源係條女啲frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就個個起勢屌個男人係敗類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩有批人都意識到唔對路<br />\n搵返原來條女扔咗個老母喺台灣<br />\n講真一個比人影曬相同人過夜<br />\n一個聲稱比人罵係雞<br />\n我先唔講兩公婆罵交好多時都罵到好難聽<br />\n都唔知單嘢堅定流<br />\n但都仲有一堆人幫條女講說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當初呀八兩仔話係比條女罵係拋頭露面出黎做鴨<br />\n所以去搵沙律談心<br />\n大家只係好朋友<br />\n唔知結局會唔會唔同呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195c9043e9d070f3d302448a30f693d42f888c48","tid":2460840,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d05d39568e7b13064a22a8d9459e0a355b9fcae0","tid":2460840,"uid":158635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"隨便囉，只係有人覺得有問題，亦有人覺得冇問題"},{"pid":"96c66e0c568cb12f0e99cda2235f1f5d53113776","tid":2460840,"uid":264117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"台灣啲新聞真係煩到嘔，唔係講福原就講對變性人大肚，妖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779d391c2972d3e57ac2854589356d345c835aa8","tid":2460840,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"555259cf454a5e21804c326c694075d9bd7ae37d","tid":2460840,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1aadd5fbba45f140bbcd91e83774f47571529d97","tid":2460840,"uid":10890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6cff21d5ecce50fec87673ba98dd3f588b772e80","tid":2460840,"uid":377617,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"之前有單新聞講咩倫敦奧運村一晚用左唔知幾多個condom"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"正常啦<br />\n大把人平時做完運動做完gym都會想扑嘢<br />\n更何況奧運選手操到咁恆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"香港有個跆拳女選手, 都出晒名淫蕩"},"citedBy":0,"reply